Class Login

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.eprize.selenium.Login

  • public class Login
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by dnewell on 3/20/16. This Test Class Logs in an existing user. It assumes it is being run immediately after registering. If this is not to be used immediately after registering it will need to be modified for the correct message. Additionally that is another use case and tests that needs to be performed given the proper facilities.
